  "instructions": [
    "Heat the vegetable oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add onions and minced garlic, sautéing until they soften and turn translucent.",
    "Fold in pecans and ketchup. Stir well to combine all ingredients.",
    "Season with salt and ground black pepper according to your taste.",
    "Cook for about 5-7 minutes or until the mixture is thickened and the pecans are crispy."
